Whiteboard: Byte 81    	  last revised by 64.152.75.182 on Aug 17, 2005 2:20 am     	
		

In 1981 there was an issue of Byte devoted to Smalltalk (SmallTalk). It was influential and gave many people their first look at Smalltalk-80. The issue has long since gone out of print, but some of the articles have been archived on the web.

   1.

      *Design Principles Behind Smalltalk *, by Dan Ingalls, as it appeared in BYTE Magazine in August 1981. (Thanks to Dwight Hughes putting this on the web.)
   2.

      An object lesson from Smalltalk --- Smalltalk: Yesterday, Today, and Tomorrow by Adele Goldberg and L. Peter Deutsch August 1991 http://www.byte.com/art/9608/sec4/art1.htm
   3.

      The Smalltalk Environment by Larry Tesler August 1981 http://www.byte.com/art/9608/sec4/art3.htm

